### Seed products
POST http://localhost:8094/api/products/seed

### Simulate orders
POST http://localhost:8094/api/simulations/orders?count=100

### Economy summary
GET http://localhost:8094/api/market-economy/summary

### Operations summary
GET http://localhost:8094/api/operations/summary

### Outbox summary
GET http://localhost:8094/api/outbox/summary

### Publish outbox in dry-run mode
POST http://localhost:8094/api/outbox/publish

### External event
POST http://localhost:8094/api/events/external
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "EXT-1",
  "idempotencyKey": "NEXUS:PRODUCTION_COMPLETED:ORD-1",
  "source": "Archive-Nexus",
  "eventType": "PRODUCTION_COMPLETED",
  "schemaVersion": 1,
  "occurredAt": "2026-07-10T00:00:00Z",
  "simulationRunId": "SIM-DEMO",
  "settlementCycleId": "SETTLEMENT-2026-07-10",
  "correlationId": "CORR-DEMO",
  "causationId": "ORD-1",
  "hopCount": 1,
  "maxHop": 5,
  "payload": {
    "orderId": "ORD-1"
  }
}
